 hometown, at the age of 34."},"et":{"1274–1308":"1274–1308","1264–Male":"1264–Surnud","1272–Male":"1272–Surnud","1275–1312":"1275–1312","1270–Male":"1270–Surnud","1275–1308":"1275–1308","1238–1270":"1238–1270","1250–1283":"1250–1283","1238":"1238","1312":"1312","1275":"1275","1264":"1264","1274":"1274","1283":"1283","1294":"1294","1250":"1250","1272":"1272","1308":"1308","1270":"1270","Napoli, Campania, Italy":"Napoli, Campania, Itaalia","Napoli, Campania, Italie":"Napoli, Campania, Itaalia"},"fi":{"1274–1308":"1274–1308","1264–Male":"1264–Kuollut","1272–Male":"1272–Kuollut","1275–1312":"1275–1312","1270–Male":"1270–Kuollut","1275–1308":"1275–1308","1238–1270":"1238–1270","1250–1283":"1250–1283","1238":"1238","1312":"1312","1275":"1275","1264":"1264","1274":"1274","1283":"1283","1294":"1294","1250":"1250","1272":"1272","1308":"1308","1270":"1270","Napoli, Campania, Italy":"Napoli, Campania, Italia","Napoli, Campania, Italie":"Napoli, Campania, Italia"},"fr":{"1274–1308":"1274–1308","1264–Male":"1264–Décédé","1272–Male":"1272–Décédé","1275–1312":"1275–1312","1270–Male":"1270–Décédé","1275–1308":"1275–1308","1238–1270":"1238–1270","1250–1283":"1250–1283","1238":"1238","1312":"1312","1275":"1275","1264":"1264","1274":"1274","1283":"1283","1294":"1294","1250":"1250","1272":"1272","1308":"1308","1270":"1270","Napoli, Campania, Italy":"Napoli, Campania, Italie","Napoli, Campania, Italie":"Napoli, Campania, Italie","lifeSummary":"Lorsque Elvira Alburia della Marra est née en 1274, à Napoli, Campania, Italie, son père, Ricone Della Marra, avait 37 ans et sa mère, Adelita de Tricarico, avait 24 ans. Elle a épousé Grimaud DE BETHZAN en 1294, à Napoli, Campania, Italie. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fille. Elle est décédée en 1308, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 34 ans."},"de":{"1274–1308":"1274–1308","1264–Male":"1264–Verstorben","1272–Male":"1272–Verstorben","1275–1312":"1275–1312","1270–Male":"1270–Verstorben","1275–1308":"1275–1308","1238–1270":"1238–1270","1250–1283":"1250–128